summary: JEEP LIBERTY. CONSUMER STATES WHEN HE OPENED ONE OF THE REAR WINDOWS, THE VEHICLE WENT INTO A SERIOUS TREMBLE AND ROAR MODE WHILE DRIVING *TGW  THE CONSUMER STATED THE PROBLEM WITH THE VEHICLE WAS NOTICED WHILE DRIVING 55-60 MPH.  WHEN HE CLOSED THE WINDOW, THE PROBLEM DISAPPEARED. THE CONSUMER STATED THERE WAS A MENTION OF WIND BUFFERING IN THE OWNERS MANUAL, WHICH ALSO STATED TO ADJUST THE FRONT AND REAR WINDOWS. *JB
